%description
The BACprior package provides an approximate sensitivity analysis of the
Bayesian Adjustment for Confounding (BAC) algorithm (Wang et al., 2012)
with regards to the hyperparameter omega. The package also provides
functions to guide the user in their choice of an appropriate omega value.
The method is based on Lefebvre, Atherton and Talbot (2014).

